						<summary>

						<p>This is also damaged. It registers a similar agreement by the <hi rend="italic">Śivabrahmaṇas</hi> of the temple to pay interest by way of paddy annually to the temple on the amount received by them by the sale of a piece of land or house-site situated in the <hi rend="italic">Tirumaḍaiviḷāgam</hi> (surrounding streets) of the god. Refers to the construction of a <hi rend="italic">guhai</hi> by one Kañjāṟan Tirunaṭṭaperumāḷ Vantoṇḍar.</p>						

						</summary>
